{% call components.section("Style") -%}
  <p>Navigation is theme-agnostic since it’s used on every page. It’s divided into three discrete sections consisting of a logo, menus, and utilities all wrapped in a background. When menus and utilities are selected, a dropdown tray expands to display various elements.</p>

